title: Billable Hours S03E08 Insane in the Membrane XviD PtL
description:
Having never had the chicken pox, Clark tries desperately, and fails miserably, to quarantine himself when an outbreak reaches employees at Fagen and Harrison. Robin looks forward to the tropical vacation she&#039;s been awarded for billing the most hours at the firm, but is unpleasantly surprised when all she gets is an old fashioned roasting. 

------------


This is the last one. Making a huge effort to grab the seventh episode from webstream before its gone for good (if it isn&#039;t already). Again awkward quality from using cable to record the show, but through various conversion-algorithms I can proudly say it looks 10,000 times better than the original quality. Its not getting any better than this :P
